        <updateDate>2020-10-26T20:12:19Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>American Infrastructure Bonds Act of 2020</b></p> <p>This bill allows the issuer of an American infrastructure bond a credit with respect to each interest payment under such bond. Specifically, a credit of 35% of such interest is payable for bonds issued before January 1, 2026, and 28% for bonds issued after December 31, 2025. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
